{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "stu-college-conversation-school-xzdw",
    "category": "pro/student/college",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xZDWpsHwLgQ",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And here we are.",
      "zh": "我們到了。",
      "ja": "さあ、着きました。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What? This isn't the convention center.",
      "zh": "什麼？這不是會議中心。",
      "ja": "え？ここはコンベンションセンターじゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "University of Herkleton.",
      "zh": "赫克爾頓大學。",
      "ja": "ハークルトン大学です。",
      "time": "00:00:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know. You did not.",
      "zh": "我知道。你不會吧。",
      "ja": "知ってるよ。まさかね。",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just take me to a college.",
      "zh": "帶我去大學吧。",
      "ja": "ただ大学に連れてって。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "A college tour to the exam.",
      "zh": "參加大學考試的參觀。",
      "ja": "試験のための大学見学だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I wanted to check out the campus in person and I definitely can't leave you at home alone after what happened last weekend.",
      "zh": "我想親自看看校園，而且上週末發生的事，我絕對不能讓你一個人在家。",
      "ja": "キャンパスを直接見たかったんだ。それに先週末のことがあったから、一人で家に置いておけないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That didn't happen.",
      "zh": "那沒發生過。",
      "ja": "そんなことはなかったよ。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What could happen if I left you at home?",
      "zh": "如果我讓你一個人在家會發生什麼？",
      "ja": "もし君を家に一人で置いたら何が起こるんだ？",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And honestly, I thought you might like seeing this place.",
      "zh": "說實話，我覺得你可能會喜歡這個地方。",
      "ja": "正直言って、君はこの場所を気に入るかもしれないと思ったんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And you do well in school and stuff?",
      "zh": "你在學校表現不錯吧？",
      "ja": "学校の成績もいいんだろう？",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I mean, not as well as I was doing at your age, of course, but this could be a glimpse of your future.",
      "zh": "我的意思是，當然沒有你那個年紀做得好，但這可能是你未來的縮影。",
      "ja": "まあ、君の年齢の時ほど上手くはないけど、これは君の未来の一端かもしれないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi. We parked?",
      "zh": "嗨。我們停車了嗎？",
      "ja": "こんにちは。駐車した？",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes? Good.",
      "zh": "是的？很好。",
      "ja": "うん、いいよ。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Take me to back!",
      "zh": "帶我回去！",
      "ja": "戻して！",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm not going to work on the Saturday!",
      "zh": "我星期六不想上班！",
      "ja": "土曜日に働きたくない！",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No! Take me back! Take me back!",
      "zh": "不！帶我回去！帶我回去！",
      "ja": "いや！戻して！戻して！",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Come on!",
      "zh": "拜託！",
      "ja": "さあ！",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You promised me ice cream.",
      "zh": "你答應我冰淇淋的。",
      "ja": "アイスクリームを約束したでしょ。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But look, I'll take you for ice cream afterwards.",
      "zh": "但是看，我之後會帶你去吃冰淇淋。",
      "ja": "でもね、後でアイスクリームを食べに連れて行くよ。",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just don't embarrass me.",
      "zh": "別讓我丟臉。",
      "ja": "恥をかかせないでね。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Never!",
      "zh": "絕不！",
      "ja": "絶対に！",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No!",
      "zh": "不！",
      "ja": "いや！",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't want to grow up!",
      "zh": "我不想長大！",
      "ja": "大人になりたくない！",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can't make me!",
      "zh": "你不能逼我！",
      "ja": "無理やりはできないよ！",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Everybody's looking!",
      "zh": "大家都在看！",
      "ja": "みんな見てるよ！",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can anyone tell me what the most important building on the college campus is?",
      "zh": "有人能告訴我大學校園中最重要的建築是什麼嗎？",
      "ja": "大学キャンパスで最も重要な建物は何か誰か教えてくれますか？",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's right.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "その通り。",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The library.",
      "zh": "圖書館。",
      "ja": "図書館です。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can anyone tell me why the library is so important?",
      "zh": "有人能告訴我為什麼圖書館如此重要嗎？",
      "ja": "なぜ図書館がそんなに重要なのか誰か教えてくれますか？",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look at this place.",
      "zh": "看看這個地方。",
      "ja": "この場所を見てください。",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "These are the fertile fields of knowledge upon which the minds of tomorrow will be growing.",
      "zh": "這些是知識的肥沃田野，明日的心靈將在此成長。",
      "ja": "ここは知識の肥沃な畑であり、明日の心が育つ場所です。",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What are you talking about?",
      "zh": "你在說什麼？",
      "ja": "何を言ってるの？",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I mean, why would you think I would like this?",
      "zh": "我是說，你為什麼覺得我會喜歡這裡？",
      "ja": "だって、どうして僕がこれを好きだと思うの？",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm 10 years old.",
      "zh": "我才10歲。",
      "ja": "僕は10歳だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm in the prime of my youth.",
      "zh": "我正值青春年華。",
      "ja": "青春の真っ只中だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, I was 10 when I started applying to colleges.",
      "zh": "嘿，我10歲時就開始申請大學了。",
      "ja": "ねえ、僕は10歳の時に大学に申し込み始めたんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know, they all reject me because I was 10, but it's good to plan ahead.",
      "zh": "你知道的，他們都拒絕我因為我才10歲，但提前計劃是好的。",
      "ja": "知ってるだろう、10歳だからみんな断られたけど、先を見越して計画するのはいいことだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whatever.",
      "zh": "隨便啦。",
      "ja": "どうでもいいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So, what are you going to do when you turn 18?",
      "zh": "那麼，你18歲時打算做什麼？",
      "ja": "じゃあ、18歳になったら何をするつもり？",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Move into the creek?",
      "zh": "搬去小溪邊？",
      "ja": "小川のほとりに引っ越す？",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And do what?",
      "zh": "然後做什麼？",
      "ja": "で、何をするの？",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Live under a rock?",
      "zh": "住在石頭下？",
      "ja": "岩の下に住む？",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "With all the ice cream I can eat.",
      "zh": "吃我能吃的所有冰淇淋。",
      "ja": "食べられるだけのアイスクリームと一緒にね。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Buy yourself.",
      "zh": "自己買吧。",
      "ja": "自分で買ってね。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What about your friends?",
      "zh": "你的朋友呢？",
      "ja": "友達はどうするの？",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You think they're all going to stay in the creek forever with you?",
      "zh": "你覺得他們會永遠和你一起待在小溪邊嗎？",
      "ja": "みんな君と一緒にずっと小川にいると思う？",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Be a little rock neighbors?",
      "zh": "當小石頭鄰居？",
      "ja": "小さな岩の隣人になる？",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Life isn't all sprinkles and hot fudge, you know?",
      "zh": "人生不是只有糖霜和熱巧克力醬，你知道嗎？",
      "ja": "人生はスプリンクルとホットファッジだけじゃないんだよ？",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You need a plan.",
      "zh": "你需要一個計劃。",
      "ja": "計画が必要だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The inscription on the library reads non-temper at medium.",
      "zh": "圖書館上的銘文寫著 non-temper at medium。",
      "ja": "図書館の碑文には「non-temper at medium」と書かれている。",
      "time": "00:02:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can anyone tell me who said this?",
      "zh": "有人能告訴我這是誰說的嗎？",
      "ja": "誰が言ったか分かる人はいますか？",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "蛤？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "それは何？",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I was looking for the great 18th century thinker Juniper Ser...",
      "zh": "我在找18世紀偉大思想家朱尼珀·塞爾...",
      "ja": "私は18世紀の偉大な思想家ジュニパー・サーを探していた...",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Get it!",
      "zh": "懂了！",
      "ja": "わかった！",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Get it!",
      "zh": "懂了！",
      "ja": "わかった！",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I need to talk to you!",
      "zh": "我需要跟你說話！",
      "ja": "話があるんだ！",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "zh": "你要去哪？",
      "ja": "どこに行くの？",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who is that?",
      "zh": "那是誰？",
      "ja": "あれは誰？",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's Kenneth, the first king of the creek.",
      "zh": "那是肯尼斯，小溪的第一任國王。",
      "ja": "あれはケネス、小川の初代王だ。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And I have to ask him about the part of the forest.",
      "zh": "我得問他關於森林的部分。",
      "ja": "そして彼に森の部分について聞かなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "His Latin phrase.",
      "zh": "他的拉丁語短語。",
      "ja": "彼のラテン語のフレーズだ。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Clack!",
      "zh": "咔嚓！",
      "ja": "カチッ！",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You just go?",
      "zh": "你就這樣走了？",
      "ja": "そのまま行っちゃうの？",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please, just go.",
      "zh": "拜託，快走吧。",
      "ja": "お願い、行って。",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Fish.",
      "zh": "魚。",
      "ja": "魚。",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is not worth the credit.",
      "zh": "這不值得學分。",
      "ja": "これは単位の価値がない。",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I need to ask you about your treasure!",
      "zh": "我需要問你關於你的寶藏！",
      "ja": "君の宝物について聞かなきゃ！",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The part of the forest!",
      "zh": "森林的部分！",
      "ja": "森の部分！",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Get it!",
      "zh": "懂了！",
      "ja": "わかった！",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah!",
      "zh": "啊！",
      "ja": "ああ！",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm so sorry.",
      "zh": "我很抱歉。",
      "ja": "ごめんなさい。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm so sorry.",
      "zh": "我很抱歉。",
      "ja": "本当にごめんなさい。",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here you go.",
      "zh": "給你。",
      "ja": "はい、どうぞ。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, you're not him.",
      "zh": "喔，你不是他。",
      "ja": "ああ、君は彼じゃないね。",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you?",
      "zh": "是嗎？",
      "ja": "そう？",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不是。",
      "ja": "違うよ。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Get it.",
      "zh": "懂了。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Kenneth?",
      "zh": "肯尼斯？",
      "ja": "ケネス？",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Shut the door.",
      "zh": "關門。",
      "ja": "ドアを閉めて。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Craig?",
      "zh": "克雷格？",
      "ja": "クレイグ？",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Craig?",
      "zh": "克雷格？",
      "ja": "クレイグ？",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He's study of philosophy.",
      "zh": "他是哲學研究者。",
      "ja": "彼は哲学を研究している。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's been philosophized by many philosophers for many years.",
      "zh": "這已被許多哲學家研究多年。",
      "ja": "長年にわたり多くの哲学者によって哲学されてきた。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Kenneth?",
      "zh": "肯尼斯？",
      "ja": "ケネス？",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nice of you to join us.",
      "zh": "很高興你加入我們。",
      "ja": "参加してくれて嬉しいよ。",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
